{"tid":2442450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持林郑月娥大大力改革选举制度","createTime":"2021-03-11T11:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T11:43:22.000Z","uid":47614,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a34858a7ffd5e276bfe10dd9f1a7ccc3d393b7ff","tid":2442450,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"點解唔支持？<br />\n<br />\n我想睇全部愛国者 親共派支配立法會<br />\n<br />\n我想睇港共全面迫害民主派<br />\n<br />\n我想睇港共直接委任特首<br />\n<br />\n我想睇國際意識到香港已經係中国一個城市<br />\n<br />\n我想睇香港失去國際地位 <br />\n<br />\n我想睇各種外資走資 <br />\n<br />\n我想睇香港本土人才移民流失<br />\n<br />\n我想睇住中共港共攬炒香港 玩火自焚<br />\n<br />\n我想睇<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">攬炒十步曲</span></strong></span>成功<br />\n<br />\n要革命 就一定會有破壞<br />\n而呢個破壞 就係中共親手造成<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷正下一盤很大的棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WOewUQF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWOewUQF.jpg&h=3f8b1e20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然黎明前嘅黑暗真係好長好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各香港人保持身心靈健康 <br />\n一齊睇住港共攬炒香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab15e34a4dbd00d4a0e8323663748ecf1693278","tid":2442450,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"樓主正5毛pr分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b515750290ee627bfc26863c5cac7ddd8a5307e","tid":2442450,"uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c